sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Ops as Operatör eller Logic App
    participant APIM as APIM
    participant CF as Common Function App
    participant Q as Service Bus Queue DLQ
    participant LA as Log Analytics

    Ops->>APIM: POST GetQueueDeadLetterSummary queue?
    APIM->>CF: HTTP trigger
    CF->>Q: Läs dead-letter summary
    Q-->>CF: DLQ counts
    CF-->>Ops: 200 + summary

    Ops->>APIM: POST GetQueueDeadLetterMessagesPeek queue maxCount?
    APIM->>CF: HTTP trigger
    CF->>Q: Peek flera DLQ-meddelanden
    Q-->>CF: Lista meddelanden
    CF-->>Ops: 200 + meddelanden

    Ops->>APIM: POST GetQueueDeadLetterMessagePeek sequenceNumber
    APIM->>CF: HTTP trigger
    CF->>Q: Peek specifikt DLQ-meddelande
    Q-->>CF: Meddelande
    CF-->>Ops: 200

    Ops->>APIM: POST GetQueueDeadLetterMessagePeekLock sequenceNumber
    APIM->>CF: HTTP trigger
    CF->>Q: PeekLock DLQ-meddelande
    Q-->>CF: Låst meddelande
    CF-->>Ops: 200

    Ops->>APIM: POST CompleteQueueDeadLetterMessage sequenceNumber
    APIM->>CF: HTTP trigger
    CF->>Q: Complete låst DLQ-meddelande
    Q-->>CF: Ack
    CF-->>Ops: 200

    Note over CF,LA: DeadLetterTimerTracker inkluderar även kö-baserad dead-letter summering i Log Analytics.
